---Folders---
handout - Assignment description and documentation
results - output from the runscript
outputFiles - where the output files from rw and mixed go.
Write-up - the write up

---Executables---
./pi-sched - A simple program for statistically calculating pi using
             a specific scheduling policy
./rw - A simple i/o bound example program.
./mixed - A program that combines pi-sched and rw

---Examples---
Build:
 make

Clean:
 make clean

pi-sched:
 ./pi-sched <#Processes> <Scheduler>

rw:
 ./rw <#Processors> <Scheduler>
 ./rw <#Processors> <Scheduler> <#Bytes to Write to Output File> <Block Size> <Input Filename> <Output Filename>

mixed:
 ./mixed <#Processors> <Scheduler>

runscript:
 ./runscript.sh

